  @{"CHR        " link CHR} Returns the character with the specified ASCII code
  @{"CLOSE      " link CLOSE} Closes the current database or all the databases
  @{"CLRRECORD  " link CLRRECORD} Clears all fields in the current record
  @{"CURRENTREC " link CURRENTREC} Returns the number of the current record
  @{"CYCLESTRING" link CYCLESTRING} Returns the string associated with the selected item
