  @{"GETFIELDSTR" link GETFIELDSTR} Returns the contents of a field as a string
  @{"GETSELECTED" link GETSELECTED} Makes a record selected with the mouse the current one
  @{"GOTO       " link GOTO} Jumps to the first closest matching record
