  @{"INDEX      " link INDEX} Returns the number of, and names of indexes
  @{"INIT       " link INIT} Initializates a variable
  @{"INSRECORD  " link INSRECORD} Inserts a new record
  @{"INT        " link INT} Rounds a number to the nearest integer and returns it
  @{"IXFIELD    " link IXFIELD} Returns the number of, and names of index fields in an index
  @{"LANGUAGE   " link LANGUAGE} Returns the name of the language locale in use
  @{"LASTPOS    " link LASTPOS} Returns the last starting postion of a string within another
  @{"LEFT       " link LEFT} Returns the left part of a string
  @{"LEN        " link LEN} Returns the length of a character string
  @{"LOAD       " link LOAD} Loads a database into the current window
  @{"LOADVIEW   " link LOADVIEW} Loads a view
  @{"LOCK       " link LOCK} Locks out user input in the current window
