   3.00b September 1994

    Major Upgrade (beta)

   - Calculated fields.
   - Extended field attributes to include:
	Mandatory
	Left/right justification
	Number of decimals
   - Indexes can allow or prevent duplicates
   - Multiple open files in separate windows
